summary: a cool retexture of banded iron armour and regular iron gauntlets and boots along with bone crown
descriptionHtml:
a cool retexture of banded iron armour and regular iron gauntlets and boots along with bone crown and also a buff of the armour that makes it a little weaker than daedric.
Hopefully will be adding a weapon and shield and two handed varient to the mod soon. works on males and females. will add file as soon as possible (tommrow) My first mod.
author: Andrew H aka AHtheking394
